title: BOOTS No7 Photo Fix Wrinkle Filler & Primer
description: This fabulous new and innovative primer reduces the appearance of the signs of aging instantly! The results can be seen in just 10 minutes and they last for up to 8 hours. A unique complex combines filling properties with light diffusing particles to smooth fine lines and wrinkles and put uneven skin tone and pores into soft focus. 1 U.S. fl. oz.
